snippet.title: Superola Champion Edition - Launch Trailer | PS5 & PS4 Games
snippet.description:
CHALLENGING RUNNER-STYLE PLATFORMING ADVENTURE

Superola Champion Edition is a challenging runner-style platforming 
adventure, in which you’ll have to guide a burger loving llama in its 
quest to defeat the Hotdog Aliens and recover the stolen hamburgers... before they get cold!

Explore 10 worlds with over 70 super challenging stages, unlock all 
the costumes and map’s secrets, fight boss battles, clear bonus rounds 
and compete with up to 4 friends!

Superola Champion Edition is available now on PlayStation 5 and PlayStation 4!

#ps5games #ps4games
